        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>some problem</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@3.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous"><meta name="generator" content="Hexo 4.2.1"><link rel="alternate" href="/ly721.github.io/atom.xml" title="Yur Blog" type="application/atom+xml"></head><style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{padding:10px 30px}</style><body><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/efbeddc5eb19" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-send"></span> next主题设置</a></p><div class="vue"><center><h3>vue项目遇到的问题</h3></center><p>在 build 项目时,报错 .plugins[0] may only be a two-tuple or three-tuple 检查配置文件babel.config.js发现 自己这样写</p><pre>plugins: [  [    'component',    {      libraryName: 'element-ui',      styleLibraryName: 'theme-chalk'    }, ...prodPlugins,'@babel/plugin-syntax-dynamic-import'  ]]</pre>应该这样配置<pre>    plugins: [  [    'component',    {      libraryName: 'element-ui',      styleLibraryName: 'theme-chalk'    }  ], ...prodPlugins,'@babel/plugin-syntax-dynamic-import']</pre><a id="more"></a><div><span style="color:red">注意：</span>在使用cdn加载elementui时，public/index.html一定要先加载vue.js再加载element-ui.js要不然组件就会无效！！</div></div><script src="/ly721.github.io/live2dw/lib/L2Dwidget.min.js?094cbace49a39548bed64abff5988b05"></script><script>L2Dwidget.init({pluginRootPath:"live2dw/",pluginJsPath:"lib/",pluginModelPath:"assets/",model:{jsonPath:"/ly721.github.io/live2dw/assets/wanko.model.json"},display:{position:"right",width:150,height:300},mobile:{show:!0},log:!1,tagMode:!1})</script></body></html>]]></content>
      
      
      
